name: Mini Drive Unit

name: Reversible Angle Motor Reverse
description: This is a compact, low-powered spin motor, ideal for driving or limited weapon uses.

description: Designed for heavy duty drive systems and other high-torque, high-velocity applications.  This motor will draw alot of electricity, so be sure your bot has the battery power to support it.

description: The Z-Tek High Powered model has a heavy-duty core and is designed to output twice the power. It draws twice as much electricity, as well.

name: DDT Burst Motor

name: Snapper II Burst Motor

name: PowerX Bidirectional Burst
